    <div class="block__content">
      
      <p>If you are at risk of becoming homeless, or have recently been made homeless, it is important to tell your local council as soon as possible.</p>

      <p>If you are in one of our featured locations, you can find out more about support available through your council here:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/bolton/">Bolton</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/bury/">Bury</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/leeds/">Leeds</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/manchester/">Manchester</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/oldham/">Oldham</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/rochdale/">Rochdale</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/salford/">Salford</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/stockport/">Stockport</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/tameside/">Tameside</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/trafford/">Trafford</a></li>
        <li><a href="/find-help/emergency-help/councils/wigan/">Wigan</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>For all other areas, visit your town hall or get more information from your council web site.</p>

      <p>If you feel you are unable to get the support you need from your council, we advise that you visit a local <a href="/find-help/category-by-day/?category=dropin">drop in centre</a>, <a href="/find-help/category-by-day/?category=support">advice services</a>, or contact <a href="http://www.shelter.org.uk/">Shelter</a>.</p>

